---
description: Security rules for games-hub
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx"]
---

- Never commit `.env.local` or any file with real API keys
- Firebase config is public (security via Firestore rules), but API keys still go in env vars
- Admin panel must require authentication before showing data
- Sanitize all user input before rendering (game names, clues, etc.)
- Use `NEXT_PUBLIC_` prefix only for client-safe values
